seo: 通达OA,文件上传漏洞,漏洞检测,安全测试
seo_en: Tongda OA,file upload vulnerability,vulnerability detection,security testing
summary: 该插件用于检测通达OA 11.2版本中的文件上传漏洞，通过模拟文件上传操作验证是否存在安全风险。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect the file upload vulnerability in Tongda OA version 11.2 by simulating a file upload operation to verify potential security risks.
